<L>__{73. the leading jolly boat}
<A>__{calamy, in the prow of the jolly boat, sees allen on the ship, signalling the turn to eastward. calamy signals to bonden in the stern of the jolly boat.}
<C>__{bonden}
<P>__{(urgent whisper)}
<D>__{starboard haul. and stroke! stroke!}
<A>__{one side stops rowing and the boat turns.}
<L>__{74. the surprise}
<A>__{a low angle, the ship coming slowly toward us. beyond, the rowers strain at their oars, the great ship rearing out of the mist above them, as though carried on their backs.}
